{"tid":2217451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[An]第一次寫game 靈感來自限聚令","createTime":"2020-09-25T12:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T13:50:07.000Z","uid":377298,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"43f5020b83b7d8ca98898ae1d2b4291a8c097569","tid":2217451,"uid":377298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"幾個月前突然想寫game<br />\n之後喺新聞見到限聚令，心諗如果有人衝埋嚟，咪可以話我超出限聚人數<br />\n跟住我就用咗呢個idea整咗個game<br />\n玩法就係避開衝過嚟嘅人，令每個地方都少於限定嘅人數<br />\n<br />\n第一次寫game，只係讀過programming嘅intro course<br />\n差唔多由零開始學起<br />\n雖然只係個小遊戲<br />\n但係都希望大家支持下，比少少意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t5_iuKA6pJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft5_iuKA6pJM&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwznO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=a5250ff2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t5_iuKA6pJM</a><br />\n<br />\n宜家淨係喺Google Play上咗架:<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wasdgames.CrowdBan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.wasdgames.CrowdBan&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwznO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=55bf8d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wasdgames.CrowdBan</a>"},{"pid":"10f98c4c0d94de771d9307c7910671e881340d6e","tid":2217451,"uid":160823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a67a2522b26b1fe4300cacbfc5bed84912592d5","tid":2217451,"uid":345839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"755e6e3b144391a684f1840843090628e53fceb5","tid":2217451,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"